.BR bfclearall (3).
.RE
.LP
.B
bfclearbit()
.br
.RS
.LP
clears one bit in a bitfield. For details, see manual page for
.BR bfclearbit (3).
.RE
.LP
.B
bfclone()
.br
.RS
