.LP
.B
bfpopcount()
.br
.RS
.LP
counts the set bits in a bit array. For details, see manual page for
.BR bfpopcount (3).
.RE
.LP
.B
bfpos()
.br
.RS
.LP
checks whether an array of bits contains a sub-array. For details, see manual 
page for
.BR bfpos (3).
.RE
.LP
.B
bfprint()
.br
.RS
