.RS
.LP
circular-shifts the contents of a bitfield. For details, see manual page for
.BR bfshift_ip (3).
.RE
.LP
.B
bfsize()
.br
.RS
.LP
obtains the number of bits of a bitfield. For details, see manual page for
.BR bfsize (3).
.RE
.LP
.B
bfsub()
